Key Match Events: Jasson Dominguez hit his second home run of the season.
Aaron Judge hit his 55th home run of the season.
Gleyber Torres hit a solo home run.
Giancarlo Stanton picked up an RBI with a hard-hit double.
Luis Gil allowed four runs on five hits while walking three and striking out five over 5.1 innings.
Clay Holmes ran into trouble in the bottom of the eighth, but Luke Weaver got out of the inning and retired the side in order to close out the game.
Post-Match Reflections: Aaron Judge expressed pride in his performance, continuing to build on his American League MVP candidacy.
